template: blog-article.html
title: Summary
subtitle: Example non-article blog page
description: "Summary of blog and article configuration as a non-article page."
content: >-

  <p>Templated pages that are related to the blog, but are not
  indexed articles, can be present in any blog sub-directory except
  <code>articles</code>; <code>tags</code> and <code>dates</code>
  should probably be avoided.</p>

  <p>If they use the blog navigation, such as this page, then they
  should be in a subdirectory of the blog path.</p>
  
